room_title: Escape room "Expedition Unknown" by Escape Quest in Washington, D.C.
room_description: You and your team have just received a letter from famous explorer and archaeologist, Dr. Silas Webb, begging you to meet him in Paris. Upon arrival at the secret meeting place, you realize something is amiss: Dr. Webb has vanished and you are trapped inside. To escape, you must solve the disappearance of Dr. Webb and complete his final Expedition, before it is too late.
